2000;;Nora;;British;;Pat Murphy;;Ewan McGregor, Susan Lynch;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nora_(2000_film);;Dublin, 1904. Walking down Dublin's Nassau Street, James Joyce meets Nora Barnacle, a young and attractive woman from Galway. Joyce, immediately in love with the young woman, offers to 'show her the city'. Nora coldly states that she has to work.<br><br>The film then proceeds to examine the relationship between Joyce and Barnacle.